%h2 Roles

%p If you want to allow a user full privileges on all content, make that user an admin.

%p= link_to("Add Role", new_role_path) if can? :create, Deadbolt::Role

%table
  - @roles.each do |role|
    %tr
      %td= link_to role.name, role_path(role)
      - if can? :update, role
        %td= link_to "edit", edit_role_path(role)
